## 5. Avalanche Detection

### Event Definition
```
avalanche_start: any cell where |ΔH| > θ_event
avalanche_end: no cells above θ_event for τ_quiet steps
```

| Parameter | Value | Description |
|-----------|-------|-------------|
| θ_event | 0.05 | Event detection threshold |
| τ_quiet | 3 | Quiet steps to end event |

### Measurements
```
size = Σ |ΔH| over all cells and timesteps in event
duration = timesteps from start to end
```

### Expected Distributions
```
P(size) ~ s^(-α)    α = 1.5 ± 0.1
P(duration) ~ d^(-β)    β = 2.0 ± 0.2
```

---

## 6. Coherence Metrics

### Kuramoto Order Parameter
```
C = |⟨e^(i·θ)⟩| = (1/N)|Σ_j e^(i·θ_j)|
```

| Level | Symbol | Target |
|-------|--------|--------|
| Micro | C_micro | > 0.4 |
| Slow | C_slow | > 0.5 |
| Global | C_global | > 0.6 |

### S* Threshold States

| State | S* Range | C_global |
|-------|----------|----------|
| Critical | < 0.5 | < 0.4 |
| Warning | 0.5–0.714 | 0.4–0.6 |
| Stable | 0.714–0.8 | 0.6–0.7 |
| Strong | > 0.8 | > 0.7 |

