## 7. Hardware Mapping (Compute)

### CPU → TIG Variables

| TIG Variable | Compute Source | Formula |
|--------------|----------------|---------|
| σ* (stress) | CPU utilization | `mean(cpu_percent) / 100` |
| R (resource) | Idle capacity | `1 - σ*` |
| H (health) | Composite | `0.4×(1-σ*) + 0.3×thermal_headroom + 0.3×(1-error_rate)` |
| W (capacity) | Throttle margin | `1 - (time_throttled / total_time)` |
| θ (phase) | Frequency oscillation | `2π × (freq - freq_min) / (freq_max - freq_min)` |

### Thermal Headroom
```
thermal_headroom = (T_max - T_current) / (T_max - T_idle)
```

| Parameter | Typical Value | Description |
|-----------|---------------|-------------|
| T_idle | 40°C | Idle temperature |
| T_max | 100°C | Thermal limit |

### Stress Tensor (Multi-Core)
```
σ_ij = correlation(load_i, load_j) × mean(load_i, load_j)
```

Cross-domain stress:
```
σ_cpu_mem = correlation(cpu_util, mem_pressure)
σ_cpu_io = correlation(cpu_util, io_wait)
```

