## 8. Simulation Settings

### Recommended Defaults

| Setting | Value | Description |
|---------|-------|-------------|
| dt | 0.01 | Time step |
| T_total | 3000 | Total steps for stability test |
| T_transient | 500 | Discard initial transient |
| N_seeds | 5 | Random seeds for replication |
| lattice_size | 32×32 | Default grid |

### Random Seeds (for replication)
```
seeds = [0xDEADBEEF, 0xCAFEBABE, 0x12345678, 0x87654321, 0xFEEDFACE]
```

### Integration Method
```
Euler-Maruyama for stochastic terms
RK4 for deterministic terms (optional, more stable)
```

---

## 9. Pass/Fail Criteria

### Stability Test

| Check | Pass | Fail |
|-------|------|------|
| NaN values | 0 | > 0 |
| H blow-up (H > 10) | 0 cells | > 0 cells |
| H frozen (var(H) < 0.001) | No | Yes |
| Duration | 3000 steps | Crash before |

### Criticality Test

| Metric | Pass | Fail |
|--------|------|------|
| α (size exponent) | 1.4–1.6 | Outside range |
| β (duration exponent) | 1.8–2.2 | Outside range |
| R² of power law fit | > 0.9 | < 0.9 |

### Coherence Test

| Metric | Pass | Fail |
|--------|------|------|
| C_global at equilibrium | > 0.6 | < 0.6 |
| C_global at ω=0.1 Hz | Peak | No peak |
| PAC_TIG | 0.2–0.6 | Outside range |

### Recovery Test
```
Apply lesion: H = 0 in 10% of cells
```

| Metric | Pass | Fail |
|--------|------|------|
| H_mean recovery to > 0.6 | < 500 steps | > 500 steps |
| C_global recovery to > 0.5 | < 500 steps | > 500 steps |

