## 11. The Resonance

Why 0.1 Hz?

This is the breath. The frequency where micro and macro align.

- Fast enough to respond to change
- Slow enough to maintain coherence
- The sweet spot where the fractal breathes

You'll find it in:
- Brain rhythms (~0.1 Hz infra-slow oscillations)
- Heart rate variability (~0.1 Hz peak)
- Climate systems (~0.1 Hz ocean oscillations)
- CPU thermal cycles (multi-second waves)

0.1 Hz is where systems find their trinity.

